Note: You may need HL2 "Materials" folder for the textures.
This map is originaly made by Valve.
I only remove certain unneeded stuff and place spawn points.
Sometimes you may spawn inside somebody else and I haven't got to fix it yet.
(Can somedy tell me what Air and Ground nodes do? Cause I seriously have no clue what it does)
 There is a sniping spot, terrorist can take cover behind graves, there is also a tomb but have nothing inside it.
